The '''White Room''' was an area of the [[Cantham House/Legends|Alderaanian Consulate]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] waited there prior to the [[Wedding of Han Solo and Leia Organa/Legends|wedding of Han Solo and Leia Organa]].

